                        <p>
                            We make the delicious coffee for the coffee lovers. We are a team of dedicated coffee fans who celebrate
                            exceptional coffee brands and roasters by providing our guests the unique opportunity to try coffee drinks
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 footer-list-29 footer-3 mt-lg-0 mt-5">
                        <h6 class="footer-title-29">Get in Touch</h6>

                        <div class="column2">
                            <div class="mb-2">
                                <span>Address :</span>
                                <p class="contact-para d-inline">B1/1, KP2, Tổ 14, đường 449, phường Tăng Nhơn Phú A, TP.Thủ Đức</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="">
                                <span>E-mail :</span><a href="mailto:CoffeeCafe2600@gmail.com">CoffeeCafe2600@gmail.com</a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mt-2">
                                <span>Phone :</span><a href="tel: +(84)-079-906-2488"> +(84)-079-906-2488</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 footer-list-29 footer-4 mt-lg-0 mt-5">
                        <h6 class="footer-title-29">Newsletter </h6>
